snippet.title: SEMP 64 | Game Jam Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist SEMP 64 (Super Easy Multiplayer Platformer 64) on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3539680/SEMP_64/

This is a super easy multiplayer platformer, or SEMP for short.
So it's a 3D platformer, with online multiplayer and it's super easy
(Disclaimer: it's actually super difficult and not super easy)

Play the Game Jam demo here: https://byxtogo.itch.io/semp64
